title: Super Chevy - April 2016
description:
English | 100 pages | PDF | 39.3 MB

SUPER CHEVY, the #1 Chevrolet enthusiast magazine, gets down and dirty for you every month with in-depth technical articles covering the hottest engine combinations, trick suspension and brake testing, and full-on restoration. There's also complete product reviews, up-to-the-minute news and event coverage, as well as four exciting Tech Talk columns written by industry experts on Chevelles, Camaros, Novas, and '55-'57 Chevys
